{"tid":879680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑老公偷食工人姐姐..","createTime":"2018-10-28T07:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T14:38:43.000Z","uid":1734,"like":5,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"267d7a0d5c6752c70583c71e11b4aae205483d86","tid":879680,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:37:20.000Z","msg":"我地生左小朋友一年 因為呀媽體弱多病 所以最近請左工人照顧小朋友 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地兩公婆都返朝9晚6 老公就政府工 比較多假期 早幾日老公放假 佢就同工人同小朋友係屋企 我返到黎見到老公同工人係放出黎 工人個樣仲好尷尬  我問老公 佢話執房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工人都幾後生 又幾好身材 好驚老公對我唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應唔應該信老公好"},{"pid":"86ef026acbd563a072d6f71fdcb819596d578acb","tid":879680,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"房出黎"},{"pid":"568d04f9b9d0d1f0f71c4ececdd698b645d575ae","tid":879680,"uid":171754,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c91e7c796c9a2e12b0a9ccfbe8bb9b3b42184c1","tid":879680,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"係房出黎可以做到咩啫<br />\n自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0354abfa8729ed8a1c27e5865320dac4903b77","tid":879680,"uid":208364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"裝cam"},{"pid":"846661339ccbffd90c2caaa6f4caa7ef49cc9e22","tid":879680,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"568d04f9b9d0d1f0f71c4ececdd698b645d575ae","tid":879680,"uid":171754,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:38:44.000Z",